olf Resort, Warri; Port-Harcourt Golf Club; IBB Golf and Country Club, Abuja; Ikoyi Golf Club, Lagos; Ibadan, Jos, Enugu, Calabar and amongst. “IGCC Asaba welcomes all golfers to come and sample our beautiful, challenging and unique golf course, then go back home and beat their chest to have walked the approximately 11000sq metres, the par 72 straight 18 holes golf course offers. “Come and enjoy the golfing experience of Asaba. Come and partake of the deceptive, but lovely topography of the course. Lots of fantastic trophies and prizes have been slated, while entertainment is assured for golfers and guests during the course of the tournament. Vanguard News Nigeria As you read this piece, Sapele Athletic Club Golf section is a beehive of activities. The 18 holes golf facility which is arguably the oldest in the country, recently converted some of its browns to greens and its playing host to over 100 male and female golfers taking part in… February 5, 2010 In "Sports" History will be set tomorrow at the University of Benin Teaching Hospital (UBTH) Golf Club when the long awaited Club Captain’s Inaugural Golf Tournament tees-off at the club golf course, Benin City. September 4, 2015 In "Sports" It will definitely be a merry Christmas celebration for 40 professional golfers who last Thursday made the cut and gave their all yesterday in the maiden edition of the on-going Dr. Emmanuel Uduaghan Pro-Am golf tournament taking place at the Ibori Golf and Country Club, Asaba. December 10, 2010 In "Sports"